        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "A titanium bezel for the office on Monday. A carbon fiber bezel for a weekend road trip. A ceramic bezel for date night. One watch, three completely different vibes.",
