            "text": "Tsarbomba did something genuinely rare in the watch world: they invented a new interaction model. The interchangeable bezel system is not a gimmick—it is an engineering achievement backed by a patent and validated by a MUSE Gold Award. Pair that with Swiss movements, aerospace-grade materials, and limited edition runs, and you get a brand that punches well above its weight.",
