        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "How does the Tsarbomba interchangeable bezel system work?",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Tsarbomba uses a patented rail-and-click mechanism. You press the release points on the case, slide the current bezel off, and click the new one into place. The entire process takes under ten seconds and requires zero tools. Once locked, the bezel is completely secure with no wobble or play.",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "h3",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Are Tsarbomba watches powered by real Swiss movements?",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Yes. Every Tsarbomba watch uses a genuine Swiss automatic movement—self-winding mechanical calibers that require no battery. The brand pairs these with sapphire crystal (front and back), anti-reflective coating, and exhibition casebacks so you can see the movement in action.",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "h3",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Who should buy a Tsarbomba watch?",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Tsarbomba is ideal for watch collectors who want variety from a single timepiece, design enthusiasts drawn to materials like carbon fiber and titanium, professionals who need one watch for multiple settings, and anyone looking for a memorable luxury gift. The interchangeable bezel system lets you shift from sporty to refined in seconds.",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      }
